# **1.1 — Materialize Local Env File**

## **Goal**

Create `.env.local` safely from `.env.local.example`, but **only after confirming `.env.local` is ignored by git**. This is a hard safety gate because secrets must never be committed. [\[phases-checklist | Word\]](https://mangupublishinghouse-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ravigopal_mangupublishinghouse_onmicrosoft_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B077D3EA2-BF7F-4980-B2CD-E8690B300088%7D&file=phases-checklist.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true)

## **Pre-conditions**

* `.env.local.example` exists at repo root.  
* `.env.local` is excluded by `.gitignore`. [\[phases-checklist | Word\]](https://mangupublishinghouse-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ravigopal_mangupublishinghouse_onmicrosoft_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B077D3EA2-BF7F-4980-B2CD-E8690B300088%7D&file=phases-checklist.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true)

## **Execution Steps**

### **1.1.a — Verify `.env.local` is ignored first**

Run:

```shell
git check-ignore -v .env.local
```

Expected result:

```
.gitignore:<line-number>:.env.local
```

If there is **no output**, stop immediately. Add `.env.local` to `.gitignore`, commit that fix alone, and re-run the check before creating the env file. [\[phases-checklist | Word\]](https://mangupublishinghouse-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ravigopal_mangupublishinghouse_onmicrosoft_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B077D3EA2-BF7F-4980-B2CD-E8690B300088%7D&file=phases-checklist.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true)

---

### **1.1.b — Copy the example env file**

Run:

```shell
cp .env.local.example .env.local
```

---

### **1.1.c — Confirm git does not track it**

Run:

```shell
git status
```

Expected:

* `.env.local` does **not** appear as staged.  
* `.env.local` does **not** appear as untracked.  
* Nothing secret-bearing is visible in git status. [\[phases-checklist | Word\]](https://mangupublishinghouse-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ravigopal_mangupublishinghouse_onmicrosoft_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B077D3EA2-BF7F-4980-B2CD-E8690B300088%7D&file=phases-checklist.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true)

---

### **1.1.d — Skim `.env.local.example`**

Check whether the example file contains keys that are **not** listed in the Phase 0 state-variable block.

If new keys appear, triage them before Phase 2:

* Required for launch?  
* Optional for later?  
* Deprecated?  
* Needs Secret Manager sync later? [\[phases-checklist | Word\]](https://mangupublishinghouse-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ravigopal_mangupublishinghouse_onmicrosoft_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B077D3EA2-BF7F-4980-B2CD-E8690B300088%7D&file=phases-checklist.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true)

## **Pass Test**

```
git status shows .env.local is ignored and not staged.
```

## **Failure Rule**

If `.gitignore` does not exclude `.env.local`, treat it as an **L4 abort** because of secret-leak risk. [\[phases-checklist | Word\]](https://mangupublishinghouse-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ravigopal_mangupublishinghouse_onmicrosoft_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B077D3EA2-BF7F-4980-B2CD-E8690B300088%7D&file=phases-checklist.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true)

## **Suggested Ledger Entry**

```
[PASS] 1.1 — .env.local created from example; git check-ignore confirms it is excluded; git status shows no secret file staged.
```

