# **Phase 11 Table Format**

Each known issue is tracked with five fields:

```
Symptom / Failure
Root cause
Agent action / resolution
Verify fix worked
Recurrence guard
```

When a new incident is discovered, append a new row with all five fields filled. [\[phases-checklist | Word\]](https://mangupublishinghouse-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ravigopal_mangupublishinghouse_onmicrosoft_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B077D3EA2-BF7F-4980-B2CD-E8690B300088%7D&file=phases-checklist.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true)

