**Purpose:** Phase 16 is a separate deployment/recovery track for **NEXUS** under repo `redinc23/centuries`. It is explicitly **parked** and **does not block Mangu Publishers**. Treat it as an independent mission tree with the same execution discipline: gates, retries, escalation, and no secret leakage. [\[phases-checklist | Word\]](https://mangupublishinghouse-my.sharepoint.com/personal/ravigopal_mangupublishinghouse_onmicrosoft_com/_layouts/15/Doc.aspx?sourcedoc=%7B077D3EA2-BF7F-4980-B2CD-E8690B300088%7D&file=phases-checklist.docx&action=default&mobileredirect=true)

