# **N11 — NEXUS Gotcha Table**

Use this before debugging from scratch.

## **CORS Error**

Cause: CORS\_ORIGIN missing exact scheme and host, or trailing slash mismatch.  
Fix: Set exact CORS\_ORIGIN and redeploy API.

## **Web Calls Localhost API**

Cause: NEXT\_PUBLIC\_API\_URL wrong or web not redeployed after env change.  
Fix: Correct NEXT\_PUBLIC\_API\_URL and redeploy Vercel web.

## **API DB Resets**

Cause: Railway volume not mounted at /data.  
Fix: Mount persistent volume at /data and use DATABASE\_URL=file:/data/nexus.db.

## **API Custom-Domain SSL Issue**

Cause: Cloudflare api proxy enabled.  
Fix: Set api CNAME to DNS-only / grey cloud.

## **Vercel Build Fails**

Cause: Root Directory not set to apps/web.  
Fix: Set Vercel Root Directory \= apps/web.

## **404 on Dashboard Routes**

Cause: Vercel deployed wrong root or app.  
Fix: Deploy the App Router app from apps/web.

